  "title": "Executive Search Consultant (Entry-Level)",
  "description": "<p><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/searchasiaconsulting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><u><strong>About the Role</strong></u><br /><br />We believe great careers are built through strong mentorship, structured learning, and long-term growth. <br /><br />As an Executive Search Consultant, you’ll gain hands-on exposure to the full recruitment lifecycle while working closely with organizations to shape impactful hiring decisions. Beyond traditional recruitment, you’llprogressively take on client-facing responsibilities, sharpen your consulting and communication skills, and develop a deep understanding of how businesses build teams for success.</p><p>We welcome graduates and early-career professionals who are curious, driven, and ready to grow a sustainable career in recruitment and consulting.</p><p><u><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Lead end-to-end recruitment across various industries such as Financial Services, Consumer & Retail, Technology, Engineering, and Legal & Compliance, positioning talent solutions to meet market needs.</li><li>Execute targeted sourcing strategies and first-round interviews to identify candidates aligned with client branding and role requirements.</li><li>Drive business growth & development through strategic client acquisition, account marketing, and long-term partnership building.</li><li>Manage negotiations and close recruitment cases by aligning candidate value propositions with client hiring objectives.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Who we are looking for</strong></u></p><ul><li>Minimum Bachelor’s degree in Business, Arts & Social Sciences, or Humanities.</li><li>No experience needed, mentorship & training provided.</li><li>Genuinely curious about people, careers, and how companies grow.</li><li>Results-driven, organized, and self-motivated to hit goals.</li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please send your latest resume to:<br /><strong>Ms Jacqueline Ng Shin Yee</strong><br /><strong>HR Director (R1104502)</strong><br /><strong>Jacqueline.ng@searchasia.com.sg</strong></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Connect with us on LinkedIn!<br /><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/searchasiaconsulting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.linkedin.com/company/searchasiaconsulting/</a></p>",
